# ===========================================================================
%NAME Samples2, Suite 2: exception test
# ===========================================================================
%DESCRIPTION
# ??????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????
Execute a query on the "nonexistent" view in VDP, which does not exist and
should therefore raise a java.sql.SQLException reporting the error.
# ===========================================================================
%EXECUTION[query]
{ ds:vdp }
SELECT DISTINCT *
FROM nonexistent
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
%RESULTS[exception] View 'nonexistent' not found
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
